title: PHOTOS: Karan Johar Finally Took His Twin Babies Home
text:
Sukriti Gumber Mar . 29 . 2017 Karan Johar 
Karan Johar embraced parenthood with the birth of his twins Yash and Roohi through surrogacy last month. Obviously, we couldnâ€™t have been any more happier for him, and are pretty sure he is going to be the coolest father to his kids. 
Being born premature, the babies were kept in the NICU in a Mumbai hospital till they were in the pink of health. ( Alia Bhatt and Ayan Mukherjee were one of the few lucky ones to meet the precious little ones in the hospital). But the wait is now over, as KJo took Yash and Roohi home earlier today. Check out these photos: A post shared by Manav Manglani (@manav.manglani) on Mar 29, 2017 at 1:12am PDT A post shared by Manav Manglani (@manav.manglani) on Mar 29, 2017 at 1:10am PDT A post shared by Varinder Chawla (@varindertchawla) on Mar 29, 2017 at 1:39am PDT A post shared by Varinder Chawla (@varindertchawla) on Mar 29, 2017 at 1:38am PDT A post shared by Varinder Chawla (@varindertchawla) on Mar 29, 2017 at 1:38am PDT 
Yash and Roohi are finally home! :) 9
